Installation: [/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]Use NMM to easily install file

[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]- or -

[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]1. download and unzip the .RAR and search for: "Rebekka.jslot"
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]2. locate your presets folder in your Skyrim Directory (ex. C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\common\skyrim\data\SKSE\plugins\CharGen\Presets)
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]3. put "Rebekka.jslot" in your presets folder.
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]4. open the game and type "^" to open the console.
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]5. type "showracemenu" to activate RaceMenu,
choose Nord race.
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]6. you´ll find "Rebekka" at the presets slider.
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]Appearance will vary depending on the meshes/textures/ENB you use.
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]I´m using a combination of
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71293/]GrimTale ENB[/url] &
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/46320/]Megatherium ENB[/url][/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]
[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]
My other presets:
